# ---- Telemetry & Data Protection (telemetry.php) ----
EasyOcrTelemetry = Telemetry & Data Protection
EasyOcrTelemetryModule = Module
EasyOcrTelemetryPurpose = Purpose
EasyOcrTelemetryPurposeDesc = Transparency about data transmitted when using AI OCR functionality for invoice data extraction.
EasyOcrTelemetryContact = Contact
EasyOcrTelemetryAITitle = Third-party AI services
EasyOcrTelemetryAIWhat = What does the AI do?
EasyOcrTelemetryAIWhatDesc = When you activate easyOCR AI, PDF documents are processed by an artificial intelligence service that automatically extracts supplier, tax ID, dates, amounts and invoice lines.
EasyOcrTelemetryAISent = What data is sent?
EasyOcrTelemetryAISentDesc = Only the content of the PDF document you voluntarily process. Data is sent only when you click the AI extraction button.
EasyOcrTelemetryAINever = What is NOT sent?
EasyOcrTelemetryAINeverDesc = ERP data (customers, suppliers, existing invoices, banking data, passwords) is never sent. Only the content of the PDF you choose to process.
EasyOcrTelemetryAIProvider = Service provider
EasyOcrTelemetryAIProviderDesc = The AI service is provided by a configurable microservice. URL and API key are configured in the Settings tab. EasySoft Tech S.L. may offer a managed service or you can connect your own service.
EasyOcrTelemetryDataSent = Data transmitted to the AI service
EasyOcrTelemetryDataPDF = Content of the processed PDF document (text and images from the PDF you select)
EasyOcrTelemetryDataLang = System language (to optimize extraction)
